                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>Legislation from 1998 reduced the restriction on access to foreign affairs
                    material from 50 to 30 years. </p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>Hellenic Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Service of Diplomatic and Historical
                    Archives, Zalokosta 3, 10027 Athens</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head>Procedures</head>
                <p>Researchers must submit an application for research to the Secretariat of the
                    Archives. The application can be found on-line.</p>
